  ('optometrist-moex-00444', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列四種不同折射率物質：水：1.33；角膜：1.37；塑膠：1.49；冕玻璃：1.52，則光在何種介質中速度最慢？', '["水", "角膜", "塑膠", "冕玻璃"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00445', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在一模型眼（schematiceye）狀態下，近視-1.00D的眼睛，眼軸長較近視-2.00D的眼睛長或短多少？［假 設為軸性近視（axialmyopia），模型眼屈光力是+60.00D，軸長是22.22公厘，空氣和房水的折射率（refractive index）分別是1.000和1.333］', '["長0.76公厘", "短0.76公厘", "長0.39公厘", "短0.39公厘"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00446', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '臨床上，加入度（Add）的意義，下列何者錯誤？', '["初配老花鏡加入度要用得少", "加入度多，則可擴大明視域", "近視眼鏡配不足，則可減低加入度的需求", "看報紙的加入度，與現代 3C 需要的加入度，不一定相同"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00447', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '陳同學右眼是以眼鏡面（頂點距離為14公厘）量出為六百度的近視眼，當林先生手持-5.00DS的透鏡，此 透鏡距離角膜10公分，讓陳同學去觀察角膜前20公分的螞蟻。眼睛要做多少的調焦（accommodation）， 才能看得最清楚？', '["+0.25D", "+0.47D", "+2.07D", "+5.02D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00448', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位遠視患者，配鏡矯正時過度矯正了2D。當病患帶著此眼鏡時，其近點（nearpoint）為20cm。請問 此遠視患者之屈光調節能力（rangeofaccomodation）為多少？', '["1.00D", "3.00D", "5.00D", "7.00D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00449', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '做紅綠平衡時，會給予患者+0.50D來做霧視（fogging），如果此時患者回覆綠色螢幕上的視標更清晰，下 一步該如何調整？', '["已經達終點，不需再調", "減少遠視（正）度數或增加近視（負）度數，直到兩邊螢幕的視標一樣清楚為止", "增加遠視（正）度數", "驗光失敗，重頭再來"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
